subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which Rajput Dynasty ruled over Rajasthan until the 20th century?
question_hi: राजस्थान में 20वीं सदबी केवल शेष राजपूती के किस तथा कैसे देखा गया है?
explanation_en: The Rathore Dynasty ruled over Rajasthan until the 20th century. They are best known for the establishment of the Meena Bazaar in Jaipur.
